POKÉMON DETECTIVE PIKACHU THE story of this wildly popular franchise is simple. Pokémons usually operate as soldiers. But this time a boy wants to use a Pokémon to become a detective and solve his dad’s death. Live action combines with animation. But be careful: there are many surprises in store. Extremely entertaining for youngsters, even parents may find that the Pokémon adventures are more exciting than they imagined. Recommended. RATING: ***